Nancy Priddy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nancy_Priddy 0 Nancy Lee Priddy (born January 22, 1941) is an American actress and singer-songwriter. As an actress, she has appeared on many television series, including Bewitched, The Waltons, and Matlock. She is the mother of actress Christina Applegate.
